ds%2Foscars-hayao-miyazaki-the-boy-and-the-heron-1235937629%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Factors%20Behind%20India's%20Gigantic%204-1%20Win%20Against%20England%20In%20Test%20Series%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20thumping%20series%20win%20over%20England%20on%20sporting%20pitches%20was%20not%20only%20one%20of%20India's%20finest%20at%20home%2C%20it%20also%20reaffirmed%20their%20supremacy%20in%20the%20longest%20format%20with%20young%20and%20old%20combining%20to%20smash%20'Bazball'%20out%20of%20the%20park.%20The%20likes%20of%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami%20were%20not%20available%20throughout%20and%20injuries%20to%20KL%20Rahul%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20after%20the%20shock%20loss%20in%20the%20series%20opener%20threatened%20India's%20enviable%20dominance%20at%20home%20but%20Rohit%20and%20Co%20found%20a%20way%20to%20put%20pressure%20back%20on%20their%20aggressive%20opposition%20over%20the%20next%20four%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20out%20of%20the%20five%20debutants%20%E2%80%93%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%2C%20Dhruv%20Jurel%2C%20Akash%20Deep%20and%20Devdutt%20Padikkal%20%E2%80%93%20showed%20they%20were%20ready%20for%20the%20big%20stage%20while%20the%20pillars%20of%20the%20team%20like%20the%20captain%20himself%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20R%20Ashwin%20also%20stood%20tall%20with%20timely%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20does%20look%20bright%20for%20a%20team%20in%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20standout%20performers%20that%20allowed%20India%20to%20maintain%20their%20upper%20hand%20over%20England%20were%20young%20opener%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20wrist%20spinner%20Kuldeep%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20India's%2017th%20straight%20series%20triumph%20at%20home%2C%20a%20remarkable%20feat%20that%20is%20often%20taken%20for%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20sometimes%20we%20just%20take%20it%20for%20granted.%20What%20is%20especially%20heartening%20is%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years%20or%20a%20decade%20or%20so%2C%20India%20have%20had%20this%20dominance%20and%20has%20been%20able%20to%20string%20together%20successful%20series%20and%20have%20not%20lost%20a%20lot%20of%20Test%20matches%20inspite%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20exposure%20that%20the%20foreign%20players%20get%20in%20this%20country%2C%20compared%20to%20what%20they%20would%20get%20in%20the%2090s%20or%20the%2080s%20or%20even%20early%202000s%2C%20before%20the%20IPL%20is%20not%20comparable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20speaking%20after%20the%20innings%20and%2064-run%20victory%20in%20the%20fifth%20and%20final%20Test%20here%20on%20Saturday%2C%20which%20gave%20India%20a%204-1%20series%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20it%20is%20a%20different%20format%20but%20it%20is%20about%20familiarity.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20English%20players%20or%20Australian%20players%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20here%20in%20these%20conditions%2C%20they%20know%20people.%20So%20that's%20made%20it%20a%20lot%20easier.%20But%20inspite%20of%20that%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20maintain%20that%20record%20and%20the%20standard%20is%20a%20real%20tribute%20to%20the%20players.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJaisball%20trumps%20Bazball%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20came%20of%20age%20in%20the%20series%20and%20ended%20up%20with%20as%20many%20as%20712%20runs%2C%20becoming%20only%20the%20second%20India%20batter%20to%20scale%20the%20700-run%20peak%20in%20a%20series%20after%20the%20great%20Sunil%20Gavaskar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20gargantuan%20numbers%20won't%20be%20enough%20to%20measure%20the%20decisive%20impact%20he%20made%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20back-to-back%20double%20hundreds%20in%20Vizag%20and%20Rajkot%20went%20a%20long%20way%20in%20keeping%20the%20English%20at%20bay.%20Especially%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20in%20Vizag%2C%20his%20209%20was%20the%20only%20reason%20India%20got%20to%20396%20in%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20with%20the%20next%20best%20score%20being%2034.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20he%20was%20able%20to%20absorb%20pressure%20and%20change%20gears%20was%20the%20hallmark%20of%20his%20batting%20and%20a%20phenomenal%2026%20sixes%20in%20the%20series%20spoke%20a%20lot%20about%20his%20power%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFitter%20and%20stronger%20Kuldeep%20adds%20more%20bite%20to%20lethal%20spin%20attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%20and%20R%20Ashwin%20bowling%20in%20tandem%20in%20home%20conditions%20instill%20fear%20and%20doubts%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20any%20opposition%20and%20they%20lived%20up%20to%20their%20reputation%20with%2026%20and%2019%20wickets%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%20operating%20at%20his%20best%20in%20the%20last%20four%20Tests%20also%20added%20to%20the%20lethalness%20of%20the%20spin%20attack%2C%20not%20giving%20any%20breathing%20space%20to%20the%20confused%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20performance%20in%20Dharamsala%20summed%20up%20his%20invaluable%20contribution%20to%20the%20team's%20cause.%20On%20a%20flat%20day%20one%20track%2C%20he%20got%20the%20ball%20to%20turn%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20others%20to%20end%20with%20a%20five-wicket%20haul%20as%20England%20collapsed%20to%20218%20all%20out%20from%20a%20promising%20100%20for%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20improved%20fitness%20has%20allowed%20him%20to%20bowl%20at%20a%20faster%20pace%20with%20a%20straightened%20run%20up%20and%20that%20has%20made%20all%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDebutants%20make%20it%20count%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWicket-keeper%20batter%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20made%20instant%20impact%20in%20their%20debut%20game%20in%20Rajkot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJurel%20got%20a%20handy%2046%20at%20the%20back%20end%20of%20the%20first%20innings%20before%20effecting%20a%20sharp%20run%20out%20of%20Ben%20Duckett%20in%20the%20second.%20He%20then%20secured%20himself%20a%20spot%20in%20India's%20next%20Test%20series%20with%20a%20rearguard%2090%20that%20allowed%20the%20hosts%20to%20get%20close%20to%20England's%20first%20innings%20score%20of%20353.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%2C%20who%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20years%20for%20his%20big%20break%2C%20felt%20at%20home%20from%20the%20get-go%20as%20he%20made%20a%20fifty%20in%20each%20innings%20of%20the%20Rajkot%20Test.%20His%20play%20against%20spin%20was%20sublime%20and%20in%20Dharamsala%2C%20he%20showed%20he%20can%20also%20handle%20the%20express%20pace%20of%20Mark%20Wood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacer%20Akash%20Deep%20had%20the%20morning%20of%20his%20life%20as%20he%20ran%20through%20England's%20top-order%20on%20day%20one%20in%20Ranchi%20while%20Devdutt%20Padikkal%2C%20who%20made%20an%20unexpected%20debut%20in%20Dharamsala%2C%20was%20all%20class%20in%20his%2065%20off%20103%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20nice%20to%20see%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20young%20India%20players%20in%20some%20ways.%20Young%20boys%20who%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%20in%20their%20ability.%20A%20lot%20of%20exposure%20and%20it%20certainly%20does%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dravid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20guys%20were%20just%20recently%20playing%20an%20A%20tour%20against%20England.%20That%20really%20helped%20us%20also%20to%20see%20which%20are%20the%20guys%20performing%20and%20doing%20well%20currently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20A%20team%20is%20that%20perfect%20bridge%20between%20these%20two%20standards%20(domestic%20cricket%20and%20international%20cricket.%20It%20really%20helps%20you%20identify%20the%20players%20who%20are%20in%20form%20and%20can%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20coach%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBumrah%20goes%20ballistic%20in%20Vizag%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20highly%20watchable%20five-match%20series%20and%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20spectacular%20moments%20were%20Bumrah's%20spell%20of%20reverse%20swing%20in%20Viza