p%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68508868.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oscars%202024%3A%20Yale%20To%20Broadway%20And%20Beyond%20-%20Da'Vine%20Joy%20Randolph's%20Journey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20ago%2C%20Da'Vine%20Joy%20Randolph%20earned%20rave%20reviews%20and%20a%20Tony%20nomination%20for%20her%20work%20on%20Broadway.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20she%20was%20the%20toast%20of%20Hollywood%2C%20taking%20home%20an%20Oscar%20on%20her%20first%20nomination%20for%20best%20supporting%20actress.%20Randolph%20shines%20in%20Alexander%20Payne's%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Holdovers%3C%2Fi%3E%20as%20boarding%20school%20cook%20Mary%20Lamb%2C%20who%20forms%20an%20unlikely%20bond%20with%20ornery%20teacher%20Paul%20Hunham%20(Paul%20Giamatti)%20and%20angsty%20student%20Angus%20Tully%20(Dominic%20Sessa)%20over%20the%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20bested%20a%20field%20that%20included%20two-time%20Academy%20Award%20winner%20Jodie%20Foster%20(%3Ci%3ENyad%3C%2Fi%3E)%2C%20Emily%20Blunt%20(%3Ci%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fi%3E)%2C%20America%20Ferrera%20(%3Ci%3EBarbie%3C%2Fi%3E)%20and%20Danielle%20Brooks%20(%26quot%3BThe%20Color%20Purple%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20think%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20doing%20this%20as%20a%20career.%20I%20started%20off%20as%20a%20singer%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20tearful%20Randolph%20told%20the%20audience%20at%20the%20Dolby%20Theatre.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20my%20mother%20said%20to%20me%2C%20'Go%20across%20that%20street%20to%20that%20theater%20department.%20There's%20something%20for%20you%20there.'%20And%20I%20thank%20my%20mother%20for%20doing%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMary%20is%20one%20of%20the%20only%20Black%20faces%20at%20the%20New%20England%20campus%20where%20the%20film%20is%20set%20during%20the%201970s.%20She%20is%20in%20mourning%20for%20her%20son%2C%20one%20of%20the%20school's%20few%20Black%20graduates%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War%2C%20and%20stuck%20on%20cam