y%20after%2013%20years%20to%20join%20the%20private%20sector.%3Cp%3EKwong%20Weng%20Yap%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKwong%20Weng%20Yap%2C%2046%2C%20served%20in%20the%20Singapore%20Armed%20Forces%20as%20a%20commando.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20joined%20the%20private%20sector%20after%20serving%20in%20the%20military%20for%2013%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20the%20risky%20situations%20he%20dealt%20with%20gave%20him%20tools%20to%20navigate%20the%20corporate%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fyap-kwong-weng-532a0546%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKwong%20Weng%20Yap%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20former%20commando%20with%20the%20Singapore%20Armed%20Forces.%20Yap%20left%20the%20military%20to%20join%20the%20private%20sector.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20employment%20history.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20interest%20in%20the%20army%20predated%20my%20enlistment.%20It%20began%20when%20I%20was%20a%20cadet%20in%20the%20National%20Cadet%20Corps%20(NCC)%2C%20a%20military%20cadet%20corps%20for%20youths%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20time%20with%20the%20NCC%20fuelled%20my%20passion%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20with%20the%20Singapore%20Armed%20Forces%20(SAF).%20I%20especially%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20commando.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20becoming%20a%20commando%20wasn't%20just%20about%20serving%20my%20country.%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20allow%20me%20to%20test%20my%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20enlisted%20in%201997%20and%20spent%2013%20years%20with%20the%20SAF.%20While%20in%20the%20military%2C%20I%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20train%20abroad%20%E2%80%94%20I%20went%20to%20Australia%20and%20spent%20time%20in%20the%20US%20under%20the%20Navy%20SEALs%20training%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20greatest%20challenges%20I%20faced%20as%20a%20commando%20was%20when%20I%20attended%20the%20SAF's%20Ranger%20course.%20The%2065-day%20course%20was%20a%20grueling%20experience.%20I%20remember%20being%20subjected%20to%20extreme%20stress%2C%20sleep%20deprivation%2C%20and%20hunger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ranger%20course%20challenges%20one%20to%20develop%20their%20leadership%20skills%2C%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20execute%20a%20mission%20with%20high%20standards.%20It%20wasn't%20just%20about%20endurance%2C%20but%20about%20motivating%20your%20fellow%20soldiers%20in%20a%20demanding%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20the%20course%20was%20an%20important%20rite%20of%20passage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELeaving%20the%20army%20for%20the%20private%20sector%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yap%20(right)%20with%20Singapore's%20then%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Force%2C%20Lim%20Chuan%20Poh%20(left).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c4ab3b6fcb546d2d4d66c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221025%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYap%20(right)%20with%20Singapore's%20then%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Force%2C%20Lim%20Chuan%20Poh%20(left).%3Cp%3EKwong%20Weng%20Yap%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20my%20mid-thirties%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20SAF.%20I%20wanted%20to%20challenge%20myself%20by%20breaking%20out%20of%20my%20comfort%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20had%20earned%20some%20small%20accolades%20during%20my%20military%20career%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20wasn't%20fully%20ready%20to%20jump%20into%20the%20private%20sector.%20However%2C%20I%20went%20ahead%2C%20sent%20out%20many%20resumes%20and%20talked%20to%20many%20different%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20now%20been%2010%20fulfilling%20years%20that%20I%20have%20spent%20in%20the%20private%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20job%20out%20of%20the%20army%20was%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20where%20I%20joined%20an%20industrial%20conglomerate%20as%20a%20general%20manager.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThen%2C%20I%20took%20a%20chance%20at%20entrepreneurship%20when%20I%20co-founded%20a%20travel%20startup%20in%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20about%20five%20years%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20I%20returned%20to%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20I've%20applied%20the%20skills%20I%20learned%20in%20the%20army%20to%20my%20career.%20As%20a%20soldier%2C%20you're%20sometimes%20put%20in%20very%20risky%20situations%20%E2%80%94%20and%20people%20and%20their%20lives%20are%20at%20stake.%20That%20forces%20you%20to%20approach%20problems%20from%20a%20completely%20different%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20take%20principles%20from%20military%20life%20and%20apply%20them%20in%20a%20different%20context%2C%20like%20business%20operations%2C%20naturally%2C%20not%20all%20of%20them%20will%20be%20relevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20areas%20align.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20you%20might%20need%20to%20make%20a%20big%20business%20decision.%20My%20experience%20taught%20me%20that%20you%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20strategic%20outcomes%20of%20what%20the%20company%20wants%20to%20achieve.%20There%20are%20times%20when%20you'll%20go%20with%20your%20gut%20and%20times%20when%20you%20need%20to%20think%20objectively%20about%20things.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20be%20very%20honest%20with%20yourself%20about%20what's%20working%20or%20not%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20SAF%20focuses%20greatly%20on%20efficiency%2C%20operational%20safety%2C%20and%20positive%20results%20and%20outcomes.%20That%20made%20me%20very%20mission-oriented%20and%20mission-driven%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20helped%20me%20when%20I%20was%20thinking%20about%20things%20like%20revenue%20and%20ways%20to%20make%20processes%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELife%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20fluid%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222611%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yap%20(center)%20participating%20in%20a%20panel%20discussion%20organized%20by%20Enterprise%20Singapore%2C%20a%20government%20agency%20that%20supports%20enterprise%20development.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c4ad4b6fcb546d2d4d6705%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYap%20(center)%20participating%20in%20a%20panel%20discussion%20organized%20by%20Enterprise%20Singapore%2C%20a%20government%20agency%20that%20supports%20enterprise%20development.%3Cp%3EKwong%20Weng%20Yap%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20can%20change%20very%20quickly.%20Major%20events%20like%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20or%20the%20US-China%20trade%20war%20can%20greatly%20impact%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20things%20change%2C%20companies%20have%20to%20change%20as%20well.%20There%20could%20be%20pivots%20in%20their%20lines%20of%20business%2C%20strategies%2C%20and%20workforce%20practices.%20You%20might%20have%20to%20relocate%20your%20business%20to%20save%20costs%20or%20to%20tweak%20your%20business%20model%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20things%20are%20a%20lot%20more%20fluid.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20adapt%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20I%20were%20to%20liken%20corporate%20life%20to%20my%20military%20experience%2C%20I%20would%20compare%20working%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20to%20parachuting.%20It's%20all%20about%20survival%20when%20you're%20jumping%20out%20of%20the%20aircraft%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20focusing%20on%20landing%20safely%20as%20you%20fly%20through%20the%20clouds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20also%20important%20to%20enjoy%20the%20journey%20while%20not%20losing%20sight%20of%20the%20mission.%20You%20might%20go%20by%20gut%20feeling%2C%20paired%20with%20an%20understanding%20and%20ability%20to%20understand%20the%20wind%20conditions%20and%20carefully%20steer%20your%20parachute.%20Sometimes%2C%20you%20have%20to%20make%20split%20decisions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20timing%20is%20always%20of%20the%20essence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20mourn%20the%20loss%20of%20camaraderie%20and%20the%20sense%20of%20purpose%20when%20one%20leaves%20the%20army%20for%20the%20private%20sector.%20And%20in%20the%20military%2C%20things%20are%20straightforward.%20You%20serve%20your%20country%2C%20you%20do%20your%20duties%2C%20you%20run%20operations%2C%20you%20do%20it%20to%20the%20best%20of%20your%20ability.%20You%20don't%20expect%20rewards%20to%20come%20back%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20it's%20true%20that%20the%20private%20sector%20is%20inherently%20transactional%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20different%20way.%20You%20want%20to%20make%20money%20when%20you%20sell%20a%20product%20or%20service%20to%20someone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20guess%20life%20is%20all%20about%20transactions.%20I%20may%20not%20like%20that%2C%20but%20that's%20just%20something%20I've%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-commando-trained-with-navy-seals-it-changed-my-life-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710114122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-commando-trained-with-navy-seals-it-changed-my-life-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kwong%20Weng%20Yap%2C%2046%2C%20was%20a%20commando%20with%20the%20Singapore%20Armed%20Forces.%20He%20left%20the%20army%20after%2013%20years%20to%20join%20the%20private%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Best%20Dressed%20at%20the%20Oscars%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710113976000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108376530%2Cimgsize-84774.cms%22%2C%22