findia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Foscars-2024-live-updates-india-set-to-kill-a-tiger-nominated-oscar-awards-2024-winners-list-nisha-pahuja-oscars-96th-academy-awards-winners%2Fliveblog%2F108375169.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Macron%20Backs%20%26quot%3BEnd%20Of%20Life%26quot%3B%20Bill%2C%20Aims%20For%20Parliament%20Debate%20In%20May%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%20on%20Sunday%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20he%20backed%20new%20end-of-life%20legislation%20that%20would%20allow%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20to%20die%26quot%3B%20and%20wanted%20his%20government%20to%20put%20forward%20a%20draft%20bill%20to%20parliament%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance's%20neighbours%20Switzerland%2C%20Belgium%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20have%20adopted%20laws%20that%20allow%20medically%20assisted%20dying%20in%20some%20cases.%20But%20France%20has%20resisted%20that%20step%2C%20in%20part%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20Catholic%20Church.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Claeys-Leonetti%20law%20on%20the%20end%20of%20life%2C%20adopted%20in%202016%2C%20authorizes%20deep%20sedation%20but%20only%20for%20people%20whose%20prognosis%20is%20threatened%20in%20the%20short-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Liberation%20newspaper%2C%20Macon%20said%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20call%20the%20new%20legislation%20euthanasia%20or%20assisted%20suicide%2C%20but%20rather%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20to%20die%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%2C%20strictly%20speaking%2C%20create%20a%20new%20right%20nor%20a%20freedom%2C%20but%20it%20traces%20a%20path%20which%20did%20not%20exist%20until%20now%20and%20which%20opens%20the%20possibility%20of%20requesting%20assistance%20in%20dying%20under%20certain%20strict%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20said%20those%20conditions%20would%20need%20to%20be%20met%20and%20a%20medical%20team%20would%20assess%20and%20ensure%20the%20criteria%20for%20the%20decision%20was%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20concern%20only%20adults%20capable%20of%20making%20the%20decision%20and%20whose%20life%20prognosis%20is%20threatened%20in%20the%20medium-term%20such%20as%20final-stage%20cancer%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamily%20members%20would%20also%20be%20able%20to%20appeal%20the%20decision%2C%20Macron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20builds%20on%20the%20work%20of%20a%20group%20of%20184%20randomly%20appointed%20French%20citizens%20who%20debated%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20concluded%20their%20work%20last%20year%20with%2076%25%20of%20them%20saying%20they%20favoured%20allowing%20some%20form%20of%20assistance%20to%20die%2C%20for%20those%20who%20want%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20push%20ahead%20with%20the%20end%20of%20life%20legislation%20comes%20after%20the%20right%20to%20abortion%20was%20enshrined%20into%20the%20French%20constitution%2C%20following%20an%20overwhelming%20vote%20by%20lawmakers%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20has%20sought%20to%20bolster%20his%20image%20as%20a%20social%20reformer%20just%20three%20months%20before%20June's%20European%20parliamentary%20elections.%20His%20party%20is%20more%20than%2010%20points%20behind%20the%20far-right%20Rassemblement%20National%20in%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710108720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fbpsjabso_emmanuel-macron_625x300_27_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmacron-backs-end-of-life-bill-aims-for-parliament-debate-in-may-5214845%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%20on%20Sunday%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20he%20backed%2