0free%20trade%20area%20consisting%20of%20four%20European%20states-%20Iceland%2C%20Liechtenstein%2C%20Norway%20and%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20great%20day%20for%20India's%20partnership%20with%20Iceland%2C%20Liechtenstein%2C%20Norway%20and%20Switzerland.%20Congratulate%20my%20colleague%20CIM%20%40PiyushGoyal%20on%20this%20achievement.%20The%20India-EFTA%20Trade%20%26amp%3B%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20(TEPA)%20signed%20today%20is%20a%20bold%20achievement.%20It%20reflects%20a%20new%20way%20of%20furthering%20international%20economic%20collaboration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20held%20meetings%20with%20his%20counterparts%20from%20Liechtenstein%20and%20Iceland%20during%20the%20India-EFTA%20meeting%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHappy%20to%20reconnect%20with%20FM%20%40DominiqueHasler%20of%20Liechtenstein%20during%20the%20India-EFTA%20meeting%20today.%20Value%20our%20regular%20interactions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGood%20meeting%20with%20FM%20%40Bjarni_Ben%20of%20Iceland%20on%20India-EFTA%20meeting%20sidelines.%20Discussed%20new%20areas%20of%20collaboration%2C%20investment%20and%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EAM%20said%20in%20a%20subsequent%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20EFTA%20has%20committed%20to%20promote%20investments%20to%20increase%20the%20stock%20of%20foreign%20direct%20investments%20by%20USD%20100%20billion%20in%20India%20in%20the%20next%2015%20years%2C%20and%20to%20facilitate%20the%20generation%20of%201%20million%20direct%20employment%20in%20India%2C%20through%20such%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20India%20has%20been%20working%20on%20a%20Trade%20and%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20(TEPA)%20with%20EFTA%20countries%20comprising%20Switzerland%2C%20Iceland%2C%20Norway%20and%20Liechtenstein%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20