p%20Yadav%20was%20adjudged%20player%20of%20the%20match%20for%20his%20seven-wicket%20haul%20and%20a%20feisty%2030%20down%20the%20order%20that%20helped%20India%20stretch%20the%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-arm%20wrist%20spinner%20said%20he%20was%20just%20trying%20to%20keep%20the%20ball%20on%20a%20good%20length%20throughout%20his%20spells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20focus%20on%20keeping%20it%20on%20a%20good%20length%20and%20that%20is%20very%20important%20for%20a%20spinner%20in%20this%20format.%20I%20was%20not%20thinking%20too%20much%20about%20what%20the%20batter%20was%20trying%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20picked%20the%20wickets%20of%20Ben%20Stokes%20at%20Ranchi%20and%20Zak%20Crawley%20here%20as%20his%20favourite%20dismissals%20from%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20bowled%20well%20in%20Ranchi.%20The%20wicket%20was%20slow%20and%20the%20way%20I%20used%20the%20drift%20over%20there%20was%20fantastic.%20I%20liked%20the%20Stokes%20wicket%20in%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20liked%20the%20Crawley%20wicket%20here%20(Dharamsala)%2C%20that%20was%20a%20beautiful%20ball.%20I%20really%20liked%20my%20rhythm%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20bowled%20England%20captain%20Stokes%20with%20a%20delivery%20that%20spun%20in%20from%20off-stump%20while%20right-hander%20Crawley%20got%20castled%20by%20his%20stock%20ball%20that%20turned%20in%20sharply%20from%20the%20fifth-stump%20line%20to%20disturb%20his%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20heaped%20praise%20on%20Kuldeep's%20work%20ethics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20potential%20and%20when%20the%20chips%20were%20down%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20(here)%2C%20he%20bowled%20really%20well.%20He%20came%20back%20and%20worked%20at%20NCA%20after%20his%20injury.%20He%20is%20putting%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20and%20the%20most%20pleasing%20thing%20was%20his%20(improved)%20batting%2C%26q