ot%20estranged%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20was%20swept%20by%20the%20Trinamool.%20Mr%20Khan%20had%20announced%20the%20divorce%20on%20camera%20when%20his%20wife%20joined%20politics%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Triamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%2C%20a%20senior%20leader%20from%20Bishnupur%2C%20had%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20from%20Trinamool%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20His%20wife%20had%20campaigned%20for%20him%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20announced%20candidates%20for%20Bengal's%2042%20seats%20today%2C%20underscoring%20its%20intention%20to%20play%20a%20lone%20hand%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20hugely%20upset%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20hoping%20for%20a%20rapproachement%20despite%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20declaration%20that%20she%20would%20reconsider%20ties%20with%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20India%20only%20after%20seeing%20the%20election%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20repeatedly%20declared%20its%20desire%20to%20have%20a%20respectable%20seat-sharing%20agreement%20with%20the%20TMC%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20always%20maintained%20that%20such%20an%20agreement%20has%20to%20be%20finalised%20through%20negotiations%20and%20not%20by%20unilateral%20announcements%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20has%20dropped%20at%20least%20eight%20sitting%20MPs%20and%20brought%20in%20several%20new%20faces%20such%20as%20former%20cricketers%20Yusuf%20Pathan%20and%20Kirti%20Azad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYusuf%20Pathan%20will%20contest%20from%20the%20Baharampur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20against%20Trinamool's%20arch-rival%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury.%20Mr%C2%A0%20Chowdhury%2C%20who%20won%20the%20s