shore-kumar-v-sekar-babu-526957.pdf%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20later%20changed%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20categorisation%20of%20castes%20as%20we%20know%20them%20today%2C%20is%20a%20far%20more%20recent%20and%20modern%20phenomenon.%20The%20State%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20184%20registered%20castes%20and%20the%20State%20is%20a%20cacophony%20of%20pulls%20and%20pressures%20by%20groups%20of%20persons%20claiming%20allegiance%20to%20one%20caste%20or%20the%20other.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20reference%20to%20the%20number%20of%20castes%20registered%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20had%20also%20changed%20between%20the%20two%20versions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20another%20paragraph%20of%20the%20first%20uploaded%20copy%2C%20the%20judge%20stated%20that%20a%20study%20of%20the%20original%20Vedic%20texts%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20experts%20at%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Kuppuswami%20Sastri%20Research%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20judgement%2C%20the%20study%20confirmed%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%20that%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%20was%20always%20used%20in%20the%20context%20of%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20moral%20values%20and%20virtuous%20living%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20There%20is%20absolutely%20no%20material%20to%20lead%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20that%20phrase%20was%20used%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Varna%20system%20or%20to%20propagate%20unfair%20and%20inequitable%20divisions%20of%20society%20in%20any%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20first%20judgement%20claims%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20research%20institute%E2%80%99s%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20corrected%20web%20copy%2C%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98only%E2%80%99%20was%20added%2C%20changing%20the%20sentence%20to%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20absolutely%20no%20material%20to%20lead%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20that%20phrase%20was%20used%20only%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Varna%20system%20or%20to%20propagate%20unfair%20and%20inequitable%20divisions%20of%20society%20in%20any%20manner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20one%20of%20her%20key%20observations%2C%20the%20judge%20had%20attributed%20%E2%80%9Cferocity%E2%80%9D%20shown%20by%20some%20people%20in%20claiming%20allegiance%20to%20certain%20castes%20to%20the%20benefits%20made%20available%20to%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20ferocity%20among%20persons%20belonging%20to%20different%20castes%20is%20also%2C%20in%20part%2C%20on%20account%20of%20the%20benefits%20made%20available%20to%20them.%20Can%20one%20lay%20the%20blame%20for%20these%20torturous%20circumstances%20entirely%20on%20the%20ancient%20Varna%20system%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20answer%20is%20emphatically%20in%20the%20negative%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20observed.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20statement%2C%20which%20was%20also%20widely%20criticised%2C%20is%20still%20retained%20in%20the%20new%20version%20of%20the%20judgement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710086074000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06152936%2FMadras-high-court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmadras-hc-reuploads-judgement-with-corrections-revises-bit-on-the-origins-of-caste%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20copy%20uploaded%20to%20the%20court's%20website%20said%20that%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20caste%20system%20were%20less%20than%20a%20century%20old.%20This%20was%20revised%20to%20say%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccategorisation%20of%20castes%20as%20we%20know%20them%20today%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20modern%20phenomenon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmadras-hc-reuploads-judgement-with-corrections-revises-bit-on-the-origins-of-caste%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adah%20Sharma%20starrer%20'Bas