20that%20while%20companies%20from%20his%20country%20currently%20face%20up%20to%2040%25%20import%20taxes%20on%20certain%20goods%2C%20the%20trade%20deal%20secures%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia-says-europe-trade-group-commits-100-bln-15-year-deal-2024-03-10%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cnil%20import%20taxes%20on%20nearly%20every%20Norwegian%20good%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Reuters%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20five%20countries%20have%20to%20ratify%20the%20deal%20before%20it%20takes%20effect.%20According%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20Switzerland%E2%80%99s%20government%20said%20it%20will%20begin%20this%20process%20immediately%20so%20that%20the%20deal%20can%20be%20approved%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20EFTA%E2%80%99s%20fifth-largest%20trading%20partner%20and%20two-way%20trade%20between%20the%20two%20amounted%20to%20%2425%20billion%20according%20to%20calculations%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20comes%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20has%20emphasised%20high%20GDP%20growth%20over%20the%20last%20quarter%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20says%20it%20aims%20to%20achieve%20annual%20exports%20of%20%241%20trillion%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia-europes-efta-bloc-sign-100-billion-deal%2Fa-68485259%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710081659000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10200722%2FIndia-efta-II-n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findia-efta-free-trade-pact-10-billion-investment-lowered-tariffs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20deal%2C%20signed%20between%20India%20and%20the%20four-country%20European%20Free-Trade%20Association%2C%20provides%20for%20reduces%20