tent%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10154424%2FGH_wnfxXsAAMWK-.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EUnder%20the%20umbrella%20of%20%E2%80%98Indians%20for%20Palestine%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20group%20of%20concerned%20citizens%20on%20March%207%20held%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20to%20highlight%20the%20voices%20of%20Indian%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20directly%20impacted%20by%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthor%20and%20activist%20Arundhati%20Roy%20sent%20a%20written%20message%20of%20solidarity%20which%20was%20read%20out%20at%20the%20meeting.%20%E2%80%9CRacism%20is%20of%20course%20the%20keystone%20of%20any%20act%20of%20genocide.%20The%20rhetoric%20of%20the%20highest%20officials%20of%20the%20Israeli%20state%20has%2C%20ever%20since%20Israel%20came%20into%20existence%2C%20dehumanised%20Palestinians%20and%20likened%20them%20to%20vermin%20and%20insects%2C%20just%20like%20the%20Nazis%20once%20dehumanised%20Jews.%20It%20is%20as%20though%20that%20evil%20serum%20never%20went%20away%20and%20is%20now%20only%20being%20recirculated.%20The%20%E2%80%9CNever%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20excised%20from%20that%20powerful%20slogan%20%E2%80%9CNever%20Again%E2%80%9D.%20And%20we%20are%20left%20only%20with%20%E2%80%9CAgain%E2%80%9D%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1064867%2Farundhati-roy-on-gaza-never-again%5C%22%3Eher%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Kumar%20of%20the%20Manesar%20General%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Union%20spoke%20at%20the%20event%2C%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20guarantees%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20its%20own%20workers%20being%20sent%20to%20Israel%20and%20who%20number%20in%20their%20thousands.%20He%20said%20Indian%20workers%20face%20harsh%20conditions%20and%20are%20denied%20their%20rights.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20because%20they%20were%20not%20getting%20even%20minimum%20wages%20in%20India%2C%20Indian%20workers%20were%20having%20to%20resort%20to%20go%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaya%20John%2C%20who%20teaches%20at%20Delhi%20University%2C%20laid%20out%20the%20shared%20history%20of%20India%20and%20Palestine%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20experience%20as%20colonised%20people.%20This%20shared%20history%20makes%20it%20incumbent%20on%20the%20working%20people%20of%20India%20to%20defend%20Palestinian%20rights.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20today%20for%20an%20international%20solidarity%20movement%20that%20is%20free%20from%20governmental%20control%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeakers%20also%20criticised%20the%20targeting%20of%20journalists%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20difficulties%20in%20reporting%20from%20there.%20Journalist%20Sujata%20Madhok%20cited%20figures%20from%20the%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%20on%20how%2090%20Palestinian%20journalists%20and%20media%20workers%20have%20been%20killed%2C%2016%20injured%2C%204%20missing%20and%2025%20arrested%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20since%20October%207%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArka%20Rajpandit%20of%20the%20Centre%20of%20Indian%20Trade%20Unions%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinian%20workers.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20between%202006%20and%202022%2C%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20GDP%20had%20plummeted%20by%2027%25%20and%2C%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ILO%2C%20prices%20of%20essential%20commodities%20have%20shot%20up%20from%20300%25%20to%20over%202000%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710065789000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10154424%2FGH_wnfxXsAAMWK-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findians-for-palestine-express-solidarity-with-those-under-siege-in-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speakers%20also%20criticised%20the%20targeting%20of%20journalists%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20difficulties%20in%20reporting%20from%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22eng