20was%20booked%20under%20appropriate%20sections%20for%20murder%20and%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20two%20communities.%20Now%2C%20two%20of%20his%20colleagues%20%E2%80%93%20Amay%20Acharya%20and%20Narendra%20Parmar%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20dismissed%20for%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20protect%20three%20passengers%20(Abdul%20Kadar%20Mohamed%20Hussain%20Bhanpurawala%2C%20Syed%20Saifuddin%20and%20Asgar%20Abbas%20Sheikh)%20and%20RPF%20Assistant%20Sub-Inspector%20Tikaram%20Meena.%20All%20four%20were%20gunned%20down%20inside%20the%20Jaipur-Mumbai%20Central%20Superfast%20Express%20on%20July%2031%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dismissal%20order%2C%20as%20reported%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2F2-more-rpf-cops-dismissed-in-train-hate-killings-failed-to-discharge-duty-9205487%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20mentions%20specific%20reasons%20for%20their%20dismissal.%20The%20dismissal%20orders%20read%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20accused%20constables%20on%20duty%20to%20provide%20security%20and%20protection%20to%20the%20passengers%E2%80%A6%20They%2C%20however%2C%20failed%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20The%20act%20of%20the%20accused%20constables%20would%20erode%20trust%20among%20passengers%20towards%20RPF%20and%E2%80%A6%20send%20a%20wrong%20message%20among%20other%20members%20of%20the%20force%20towards%20indiscipline.%20To%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20repetition%20of%20the%20same%2C%20retaining%20the%20constables%20in%20the%20force%20despite%20their%20failure%20to%20discharge%20their%20duty%20would%20be%20fatal%20for%20RPF.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20says%20Acharya%20is%20dismissed%20because%20he%20hid%20in%20the%20washroom%20of%20S-4%20coach%20instead%20of%20intervening.%20He%20saw%20Chaudhary%20removing%20the%20rifle%E2%80%99s%20safety%20catch%2C%20but%20left%20him%20alone%20with%20ASI%20Tikaram%20Meena%2C%20who%20was%20later%20killed%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20physically%20present%20at%20the%20time%20when%20Chaudhary%20took%20a%20passenger%20hostage%20at%20gunpoint%20in%20front%20of%20him%2C%20led%20him%20to%20another%20coach%2C%20and%20eventually%20killed%20him.%20Parmar%20too%20had%20hidden%20behind%20other%20passengers%20instead%20of%20intervening%2C%20the%20dismissal%20order%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Acharya%20is%20the%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Parmar%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20witnesses%20in%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaudhary%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20right%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20was%20moved%20to%20Akola%20prison%20after%20the%20RPF%20cited%20%E2%80%9Cthreat%20to%20his%20life%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20transfer.%20His%20lawyer%2C%20however%2C%20has%20moved%20an%20application%20seeking%20his%20transfer%20to%20a%20prison%20in%20Mumbai%20or%20neighbouring%20Thane%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710061503000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F10165435%2Fimage-1058.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftwo-rpf-constables-dismissed-in-train-hate-killings-case-for-failing-to-discharge-duties%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RPF%20constable%20Chetansinh%20Chaudhary%20was%20caught%20on%20camera%20hurling%20abuses%20at%20passengers%20from%20Muslim%20communities%20and%20gunning%20them%20down%20in%20July%20last%20year.%20He%20had%20been%20arrested%20immediately.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftwo-rpf-constables-dismissed-in-train-hate-killings-case-for-failing-to-discharge-duties%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%20and%20West%20Bengal%20BJP%20MPs%20Quit%20Party%2C%20Former%20Joins%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10134916%2FPhotoJet.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20MP%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Hisar%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20Brijendra%20Singh%20left%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBrijendraSpeaks%2Fstatus%2F1766706322727117222%5C%22%3Eciting%20%E2%80%9Ccompelling%20political%20reasons%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2010).%20He%20has%20joined%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20joined%20the%20Congress%20on%20Sunday%20following%20a%20visit%20to%20party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1766739512573505998%5C%22%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20held%20by%20the%20Congress%20on%20Sunday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Singh%20said%20he%20decided%20to%20quit%20the%20BJP%20following%20disagreements%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20those%20of%20farmers%2C%20the%20Agniveer%20program%20and%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20women%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20NDTV%20said%20that%20Congress%20sources%20hinted%20the%20party%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrijendra-singh-hisar-mp-and-son-of-veteran-politician-birender-singh-resigns-from-bjp-may-join-congress-5211003%5C%22%3Elikely%20field%20Singh%20as%20its%20candidate%20from%20Hisar%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20upcoming%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-constituencies%2Fharyana%2Fhisar%5C%22%3Eindia.gov%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Singh%20is%20a%20former%20bureaucrat%20of%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service.%20He%20voluntarily%20resigned%20in%202019%20and%20won%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20from%20Hisar%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20with%20a%20little%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-constituencies%2Fharyana%2Fhisar%5C%22%3E51%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20closest%20contestant%20was%20the%20Jannayak%20Janata%20Party%20(JJP)%E2%80%99s%20Dushyant%20Chautala%2C%20who%20is%20now%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20father%20Birender%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Haryana%20between%202016%20and%202020%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh%2Fbjp-mp-brijendra-singh-joins-congress-father-chaudhary-birender-singh-may-follow-him-9206020%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cmay%20also%20join%20the%20Congress%20later%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20citing%20sources%20close%20to%20the%20senior%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirender%20Singh%20opposed%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20JJP%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Flok-sabha-polls-birender-singh-and-dushyant-chautala-clash-over-alliance-issues-and-uchana-kalan-seat%2Farticleshow%2F108353749.cms%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20threatened%20in%20October%20to%20leave%20the%20BJP%20if%20it%20continued%20allying%20with%20the%20JJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWest%20Bengal%20MP%20resigns%20from%20BJP%2C%20says%20will%20not%20join%20another%20party%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20MP%20from%20the%20Jhargram%20constituency%20Kunar%20Hembram%20quit%20the%20BJP%20on%20Friday%20citing%20personal%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20leave%20my%20party%20for%20personal%20reasons.%20It%20is%20not%20like%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20party%20will%20suffer%20a%20loss%20or%20its%20work%20will%20get%20stuck%20if%20I%20move%20away.%20The%20BJP%20is%20a%20national%20