s%20His%20Dissent%20Within%20the%20EC%3F%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20Asks%20President%20to%20Probe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25220532%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-10.04.47%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFormer%20secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20has%20written%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20status%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Farun-goel-resigns-election-commission-of-india-down-to-just-one-member-on-election-eve%5C%22%3Eresignation%20of%20election%20commissioner%20Arun%20Goel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20has%20left%20the%20commission%20%E2%80%93%20usually%20comprising%20three%20members%20%E2%80%93%20with%20just%20one%2C%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoel%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20Sarma%20points%20out%2C%20has%20raised%20multiple%20questions%2C%20including%20whether%20the%20election%20commissioner%20had%20raised%20questions%20over%20the%20way%20things%20were%20being%20done%20in%20the%20commission.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20has%20also%20been%20in%20the%20limelight%20recently%20because%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20with%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20missing%20the%20Supreme%20Court-given%20deadline%20by%20which%20it%20had%20to%20reveal%20details%20of%20all%20bonds%20purchased%20to%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20text%20of%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20letter%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%5CnFormer%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%3Cbr%3E%5CnSmt.%20Droupadi%20Murmu%3Cbr%3E%5CnHon%E2%80%99ble%20President%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERespected%20Rashtrapati%20Ji%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKindly%20refer%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2024%2F03%2Fletter-to-president-of-india-non-transparency-of-funding-through-electoral-bonds-appointment-of-political-nominees-on-the-boards-of-sbi-bel-ecil-and-violating-norms-of-appointment-of-election-comm%2F%5C%22%3Emy%20letter%20of%207th%20March%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20attempts%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20political%20executive%20to%20deviate%20from%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20appointment%20of%20Election%20Commissioners%2C%20the%20contentious%20Electoral%20Bonds%20scheme%20(EBS)%20and%20its%20planting%20BJP%20nominees%20on%20the%20Boards%20of%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Ltd%20(BEL)%2C%20Electronics%20Corporation%20India%20Ltd%20(ECIL)%20and%20the%20SBI%20evidently%20to%20interfere%20at%20every%20stage%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20one%20way%20or%20the%20other%2C%20which%20in%20my%20view%20vitiates%20the%20sanctity%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20Election%20Commissioner%20has%20recently%20retired%20and%20the%20political%20executive%20is%20trying%20to%20select%20a%20candidate%20of%20its%20choice%20to%20succeed%20him.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20find%20that%20Shri%20Arun%20Goel%2C%20the%20third%20Election%20Commissioner%20has%20tendered%20his%20resignation%20prematurely%2C%20though%20his%20term%20is%20due%20to%20expire%20only%20in%202027.%20Shri%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20accepted%20by%20the%20government%20in%20an%20undue%20hurry%20on%20the%209th%20of%20March%2C%202024%20and%20the%20same%20was%20notified%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Justice%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20leaves%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20limping%20with%20only%20one%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20namely%2C%20Shri%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20to%20oversee%20the%20ensuing%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20transpired%20thus%20far%20is%20too%20serious%20a%20matter%20that%20casts%20a%20shadow%20on%20the%20entire%20electoral%20process%20on%20which%20some%20of%20us%20and%20many%20political%20parties%20have%20expressed%20our%20concerns%20time%20and%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20view%2C%20the%20abrupt%20and%20somewhat%20inexplicable%20exit%20of%20Shri%20Goel%20raises%20the%20following%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20Shri%20Goel%20express%20his%20dissent%20on%20the%20way%20the%20political%20executive%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20several%20ways%20vitiating%20its%20sanctity%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20Shri%20Goel%20express%20doubts%20about%20the%20efficacy%20of%20the%20use%20of%20EVMs%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20he%20express%20his%20concern%20at%20the%20way%20the%20political%20executive%20has%20pressured%20the%20SBI%20not%20to%20disclose%20the%20details%20of%20the%20EBS%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWas%20there%20any%20proposal%20from%20Shri%20Goel%20to%20freeze%20the%20residual%20amounts%20received%20by%20the%20political%20parties%20under%20the%20EBS%20to%20prevent%20their%20use%20in%20the%20ensuing%20elections%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20Shri%20Goel%20propose%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20nominees%20from%20the%20Boards%20of%20BEL%2C%20ECIL%20and%20SBI%20be%20withdrawn%20to%20maintain%20the%20sanctity%20the%20electoral%20process%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20Shri%20Goel%20express%20his%20dissent%20on%20any%20other%20matter%20that%20would%20have%20displeased%20the%20political%20executive%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20the%20highest%20within%20the%20political%20executive%20force%20Shri%20Goel%20to%20tender%20his%20resignation%20to%20clear%20the%20way%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20machinations%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20earnestly%20believe%20that%20the%20nation%20expects%20an%20independent%20inquiry%20into%20the%20above%20questions%20as%20they%20concern%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20democratic%20processes%20in%20India%20and%20the%20future%20of%20our%20democracy%20itself.%20Such%20an%20inquiry%20needs%20to%20be%20independent%20of%20the%20political%20executive%20and%20preferably%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20entrusted%20by%20your%20office%20to%20a%20panel%20of%20the%20sitting%20members%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPending%20such%20an%20enquiry%2C%20your%20office%2C%20invoking%20the%20authority%20under%20the%20Constitution%2C%20order%20that%20(i)%20no%20announcement%20of%20the%20election%20schedule%20be%20made%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20(ii)%20no%20policy%20decisions%2F%20announcements%20be%20made%20by%20the%20political%20executive%2C%20and%20(iii)%20no%20expenditure%20should%20be%20incurred%20by%20any%20political%20party%20from%20the%20funds%20received%20under%20the%20EBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERespected%20Rashtrapati%20Ji%2C%20your%20intervention%20at%20this%20critical%20juncture%20in%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20nation%20is%20necessary%20and%20perhaps%20unavoidable%20to%20preserve%20the%20democratic%20character%20of%20our%20Constitution%20and%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMay%20I%2C%20as%20a%20senior%20citizen%2C%20deeply%20concerned%20with%20the%20future%20of%20our%20democracy%2C%20appeal%20to%20you%20to%20step%20in%2C%20act%20decisively%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20dreams%20of%20Dr%20B%20R%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20other%20framers%20of%20our%20Constitution%20are%20fulfilled%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERespectfully%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%5Cn10th%20March%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710055194000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25220532%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-10.04.47%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdid-arun-goel-express-his-dissent-within-the-ec-e-a-s-sarma-asks-president-to-probe%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDid%20the%20highest%20within%20the%20political%20executive%20force%20Shri%20Goel%20to%20tender%20his%20resignation%20to%20clear%20the%20way%20for%20the%20ruling%20party's%20machinations%3F%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A71%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdid-arun-goel-express-his-dissent-within-the-ec-e-a-s-sarma-asks-president-to-probe%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boris%20Johnson%20flew%20to%20Venezuela%20for%20secret%20talks%20-%20and%20texted%20Cameron%20en%20route%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710053160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F70x70%2Fskynews-boris-johnson-nicolas-maduro_6485451.jpg%3F20240310074917%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fboris-johnson-flew-to-venezuela-for-talks-with-president-nicolas-maduro-13091597%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boris%20Johnson%20flew%20to%20Venezuela%20last%20month%20to%20meet%20the%20country's%20controversial%20leader%20Nicolas%20Maduro.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A323%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fboris-johnson-flew-to-venezuela-for-talks-with-president-nicolas-maduro-13091597%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fboris-johnson-flew-to-venezuela-for-talks-with-president-nicolas-maduro-13091597%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fboris-johnson-flew-to-venezuela-for-talks-with-president-nicolas-maduro-13091597%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Royal%20Prerogative%2C%20the%20British%20Empire%20in%20India%20and%20the%20Jurisprudence%20of%20Plunder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10115615%2F16446.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpted%20with%20permission%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20King%E2%80%99s%20Plunder%2C%20The%20King%E2%80%99s%20Bodies%3A%20Prize%20Laws%2C%20The%20British%20Empire%20and%20the%20Modern%20Legal%20Order%3Cem%3E%C2%A0by%20Rahul%20Govind.%20Published%20by%20Tulika%20Books%20and%20distributed%20internationally%20by%20Columbia%20University%20Press.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20book%20establishes%20the%20centrality%20of%20forms%20of%20royal%20authority%20to%20the%20conquests%20of%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20from%201600%20to%201900.%20A%20critical%20aspect%20of%20such%20conquests%20was%20the%20jurisprudence%20of%20plunder%20or%20%E2%80%9Cprize%20law%E2%80%9D%20concerning%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20acquisition%20of%20property%20from%20enemies%20during%20hostilities%20and%20war%20and%20its%20distribution%20among%20the%20victors.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20question%20revolved%20around%20the%20spoils%20of%20victory%20with%20no%20recognition%20of%20any%20rights%20of%20the%20vanquished.%20While%20parliamentary%20statutes%20on%20prize%20existed%20from%20the%20late%2017th%20century%2C%20it%20was%20well-recognised%20that%20the%20original%20right%20to%20prize%20belonged%20to%20the%20King%2FQueen%20as%20part%20of%20his%2Fher%20rights%20to%20conquest%3B%20a%20right%20which%20could%20be%20exercised%20independent%20of%20parliament.%20As%20this%20book%20argues%2C%20specific%20royal%20grants%20to%20prize%20money%20authorised%20the%20great%20territorial%20conquests%20of%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20in%20India.%20Though%20initially%20concerned%20with%20maritime%20warfare%2C%20prize%20law%20jurisprudence%20was%20transferred%20to%20territorial%20%E2%80%98acquisitions%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20context%20of%20India.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBy%20focusing%20on%20the%20sources%20and%20mechanics%20of%20prize%20law%20as%20central%20to%20imperial%20conquest%2C%20the%20book%20argues%20for%20the%20impossibility%20of%20separating%20England%20and%20imperial%20conquests%20by%20underlining%201)%20the%20central%20unifying%20role%20of%20monarchy%20across%20the%20range%20of%20jurisdictions%20that%20characterised%20the%20British%20Empire%20where%20political%20identity%20lay%20in%20personal%20allegiance%20and%20not%20in%20any%20notion%20of%20citizenship%20and%202)%20the%20nexus%20binding%20a%20specific%20jurisprudence%20of%20warfare%2C%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98trade%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20international%20law%2C%20all%20of%20which%20were%20tethered%20to%20an%20agenda%20of%20conquest%2C%20in%20the%20making%20of%20modern%20state%20systems%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20book%20thereby%20shows%20that%20the%20very%20methods%20of%20modern%20jurisprudence%20and%20political%20philosophy%20as%20to%20be%20found%20in%20figures%20from%20Jeremy%20Bentham%20to%20John%20Stuart%20Mill%20lies%20in%20the%20obfuscation%20and%20concealment%20of%20this%20history.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20works%20on%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20and%20its%20conquests%20in%20the%20eighteenth%20century%20appear%20to%20give%20little%20thought%20to%20prize%2C%20prize%20money%20and%20plunder.%20The%20crucial%20legitimizing%20and%20governing%20law%20on%20prize%20money%2C%20sealed%20by%20His%20Majesty%20King%20George%20the%20Second%2C%20could%20be%20traced%20to%20September%C2%A01757%20and%20January%201758%2C%20where%20the%20Company%20was%20granted%20powers%20to%20%E2%80%98cede%2C%20restore%20or%20dispose%20of%C2%A0any%20fortresses%20or%20any%20fortresses%20districts%20or%20territories%2C%20acquired%20by%20the%20conquest%20from%20any%20of%20the%C2%A0said%20Indian%20princes%20or%20governments%E2%80%99.%20The%20letters-patent%20of%20September%201757%20and%20January%201758%20%5BPrize%20charters%5D%20did%20not%20emerge%20%3Cem%3Ein%20vacuo%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20was%20the%20response%20to%20applications%20that%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20had%20made%20in%201756%20to%20the%20attorney%20and%20solicitor%20generals%2C%20the%20pre-eminent%20law%20officers%20of%20the%20Crown%2C%20who%20in%20turn%20had%20forwarded%20the%20application%20with%20suitable%20recommendation%20and%20comment%20to%C2%A0William%20Pitt%2C%20one%20of%20the%20secretaries%20of%20the%20Crown%2C%20to%20be%20in%20turn%20forwarded%20to%20the%20King.%20With%20the%C2%A0application%20the%20law%20officers%20appended%20their%20own%20draft%20of%20what%20would%20become%20in%20essence%20the%C2%A0letters-patent%20of%201757%20and%201758.%20In%20the%20applications%20of%20the%20East%20India%20Company%2C%20and%20the%20response%C2%A0of%20the%20attorney%20and%20solicitor%20general%2C%20one%20might%20glean%20the%20germ%20of%20the%20problems%20that%20collected%C2%A0again%20in%20the%20dispute%20between%20Company%20officials%20and%20the%20Court%20of%20Directors%2C%20and%20of%20course%20the%C2%A0fraught%20contested%20tendons%20of%20the%20British%20Empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Company%20had%20written%20to%20His%20Majesty%20on%2011%20October%201756%20with%20a%20request.%20Alluding%20to%C2%A0the%20war%20with%20the%20kingdom%20of%20France%20and%20the%20collusion%20%E2%80%93%20possible%2C%20actual%20and%20imaginary%20%E2%80%93%20between%C2%A0the%20latter%20and%20the%20local%20rulers%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20petitioners%20pointed%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20the%20course%20of%C2%A0such%20war%20that%20has%20or%20may%20occur%2C%20in%20so%20far%20as%20all%20conquests%20were%20vested%20directly%20in%20him%2C%20His%C2%A0Majesty%20in%20his%20sovereignty%20kindly%20grant%20the%20right%2C%20to%20capture%20and%20recapture%2C%20%E2%80%98for%20their%20own%20%5Bthe%C2%A0Company%E2%80%99s%5D%20use%2C%20all%20such%20plunder%20and%20booty%2C%20ships%2C%20vessels%2C%20goods%2C%20merchandize%2C%20treasure%20and%C2%A0other%20things%20whatsoever%2C%20which%20may%20be%20taken%20by%20any%20of%20your%20petitioners%20land%20or%20sea%20forces%20from%C2%A0any%20of%20your%20majesty%E2%80%99s%20enemies%2C%20or%20from%20the%20Indian%20enemies%20of%20your%20petitioners%E2%80%99.%20Unless%20such%C2%A0right%20was%20granted%2C%20the%20petition%20argued%2C%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20the%20armies%20that%20were%C2%A0required%20for%20the%20carrying%20out%20of%20such%20trade%20in%20the%20east.%20Encouragement%20to%20trade%20was%20conditional%20on%C2%A0the%20encouragement%20that%20could%20be%20given%20to%20those%20engaged%20in%20the%20arts%20of%20war.%20This%20requesting%20of%C2%A0powers%20over%20the%20use%20and%20disposal%20of%20territories%20and%20objects%20acquired%20in%20the%20course%20of%20war%2C%20treaty%20or%C2%A0grant%20with%20local%20principalities%2C%20was%20of%20course%20always%20subject%20to%20His%20Majesty%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98right%20of%C2%A0sovereignty%E2%80%99.%20The%20Company%20in%20its%20applications%20had%20more%20concrete%20questions%20regarding%20the%20norms%C2%A0to%20be%20followed%2C%20specifically%20in%20the%20distribution%20of%20prize%20between%20Admiral%20Watson%2C%20as%20representative%20of%20His%20Majesty%2C%20and%20the%20Company%20officers%20in%20the%20recent%20case%20of%20Gheria%20and%C2%A0Calcutta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20326px)%2085vw%2C%20326px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10115034%2FThe-Kings-Plunder-The-Kings-Bodies-Front-cover.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22326%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10115034%2FThe-Kings-Plunder-The-Kings-Bodies-Front-cover.jpg%20811w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10115034%2FThe-Kings-Plunder-The-Kings-Bodies-Front-cover-203x300.jpg%20203w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10115034%2FThe-Kings-Plunder-The-Kings-Bodies-Front-cover-692x1024.jpg%20692w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700974%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22483%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%20Govind%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20King%E2%80%99s%20Plunder%2C%20The%20King%E2%80%99s%20Bodies%3A%20Prize%20Laws%2C%20The%20British%20Empire%20and%20the%20Modern%20Legal%20Order%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ETulika%20Books%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20response%20and%20considered%20suggestions%20of%20the%20law%20officers%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%C2%A0Company%20asked%20whether%20its%20actions%20were%20governed%20by%20the%20lately%20promulgated%20Act%20of%201756%2C%C2%A0passed%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20war%20with%20France.%20Writing%20on%2016%20August%201757%2C%20the%20law%20officers%20were%C2%A0responding%20to%20requests%20regarding%20the%20re-taking%20of%20Calcutta%2C%20and%20not%20a%20post-Plassey%20settlement.%C2%A0They%20wrote%20that%20in%20their%20considered%20opinion%2C%20the%20said%20Act%20of%201756%20referred%20only%20to%20the%20war%20(with%C2%A0France)%20and%20could%20not%20be%20applicable%20to%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Company%E2%80%99s%20relations%20with%20powers%20in%20the%C2%A0subcontinent.%20And%20so%2C%20the%20most%20apposite%20way%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20Company%E2%80%99s%20question%20regarding%20its%C2%A0authority%20in%20such%20relations%20with%20local%20powers%2C%20in%20the%20event%20of%20war%20and%20with%20regard%20to%20prize%2C%20would%C2%A0be%20to%20apply%20and%20request%20the%20requisite%20letters-patent%20from%20His%20Majesty.%20With%20regard%20to%20what%20is%20re-taken%2C%20the%20law%20officers%20took%20the%20view%20that%20as%20far%20as%20the%20territory%20of%20Calcutta%20was%20concerned%2C%20it%C2%A0would%20be%20restored%20to%20the%20Company.%20However%2C%20%E2%80%98All%20places%20newly%20conquered%20accrue%20to%20his%C2%A0sovereignty%20and%20is%20vested%20in%20his%20majesty%20by%20right%20of%20conquest.%E2%80%99%20All%20movable%20goods%20that%20had%20been%C2%A0altered%20while%20in%20the%20possession%20of%20the%20enemy%20as%20well%20as%20newly%20acquired%20movable%20goods%20would%C2%A0belong%20to%20His%20Majesty%2C%20%E2%80%98in%20whose%20name%20and%20under%20whose%20protection%2C%20and%20by%20the%20assistance%20of%C2%A0whose%20fleet%2C%20the%20same%20is%20regained%E2%80%99.%20These%20suggestions%20led%20to%20the%20letters-patent%20issued%20in%C2%A0September%201757.%20The%20Company%20in%20the%20meantime%20had%20written%20to%20Fort%20St%20George%20that%20they%20had%20been%C2%A0given%20a%20specific%20grant%20by%20the%20King%2C%20commending%20the%20agreement%20between%20Admiral%20Watson%20and%20the%C2%A0Secret%20Committee%20which%20stated%20that%20all%20plunder%20and%20booty%20would%20be%20deposited%20until%20His%20Majesty%C2%A0made%20his%20pleasure%20known.%20The%20result%20%E2%80%93%20the%20letters-patent%20of%20September%201757%20%E2%80%93%20was%20therefore%20sent%C2%A0to%20the%20subcontinent.%20However%2C%20in%20response%20to%20further%20petitions%20and%20requests%20for%20further%C2%A0clarifications%2C%20on%2024%20December%2C%20the%20law%20officers%20elaborated%20on%20the%20urgent%20questions%20of%C2%A0sovereignty%20and%20prize.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20making%20no%20specific%20reference%20to%20Plassey%20although%20writing%20in%20a%20vein%20that%20would%C2%A0encompass%20actions%20such%20as%20the%20Battle%20of%20Plassey%2C%20the%20law%20officers%20reiterated%20that%20all%20conquests%20as%C2%A0such%20were%20vested%20with%20His%20Majesty%2C%20as%20also%20specific%20goods%20and%20items%20acquired%20therein.%20However%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%98in%20respect%20to%20such%20places%20as%20have%20been%20or%20shall%20be%20acquired%20by%20treaty%20or%20grant%20from%20the%20Mogul%20or%C2%A0any%20of%20the%20Indian%20princes%20or%20governments%2C%20your%20majesty%E2%80%99s%20letters-patent%20are%20not%20necessary%2C%20the%C2%A0property%20of%20the%20soil%20vesting%20in%20the%20company%20by%20the%20Indian%20grants%2C%20subject%20to%20only%20your%20majesty%E2%80%99s%C2%A0right%20of%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20settlements%20as%20English%20settlements%2C%20and%20over%20the%20inhabitants%20as%C2%A0English%20subjects%2C%20who%20carry%20with%20them%20your%20majesty%E2%80%99s%20laws%2C%20wherever%20they%20form%20colonies%20and%C2%A0receive%20your%20majesty%E2%80%99s%20protection%2C%20by%20virtue%20of%20your%20royal%20charters%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6%C2%A0Allegiance%20was%20owed%20to%20the%20King%20despite%20the%20possible%20diversity%20of%20place%20and%C2%A0law.%20The%20law%20officers%20clearly%20wanted%20to%20deny%20the%20Company%20the%20sovereign%20authority%20to%20carry%20out%C2%A0conquest%20and%20make%20peace%2C%20which%20ultimately%20vested%20in%20His%20Majesty%E2%80%93%20specifically%2C%20His%20Majesty%E2%80%99s%C2%A0prerogative.%20Perhaps%20more%20significant%20however%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Company%20were%C2%A0being%20derived%20exclusively%20from%20a%20royal%20charter%20%5Bthe%20royal%20letters-patents%20referred%20to%20above%5D%20and%20not%20from%20any%20%5Bparliamentary%5D%20Prize%20statute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20precariousness%20and%20complexity%20of%20deciding%20prize%20and%20its%20legitimate%20claimants%20is%20evident%C2%A0in%20the%20attack%2C%20capture%20and%20plunder%20of%20the%20properties%20in%20Fort%20Vidyadurg%20in%20Benaras%20in%201776%2C%C2%A0amounting%20to%20300%2C000%20pounds.%20This%20incident%20received%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20publicity%20in%20the%20trial%20of%C2%A0Warren%20Hastings%2C%20linked%20as%20it%20was%20to%20what%20was%20called%20the%20charge%20of%20Benaras.%20After%20attempting%20to%C2%A0arrest%20Raja%20Chait%20Singh%2C%20the%20English%20attacked%20his%20fortress%2C%20Vidyadurg%2C%20where%20the%20raja%E2%80%99s%20mother%C2%A0and%20wife%20lived.%20It%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20housed%20much%20of%20Chait%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20property%20and%20money.%20The%C2%A0course%20of%20the%20trial%20revealed%20that%20Hastings%20had%20allowed%20Major%20Popham%20to%20capture%2C%20plunder%20and%C2%A0divide%20whatever%20property%20was%20found%20in%20the%20fortress.%20This%20was%20indicated%20in%20a%20private%20letter%20to%20Major%C2%A0Popham%20which%20sanctioned%20the%20plunder.%20Later%20Hastings%20tried%20to%20retrieve%20the%20divided%20plunder%20but%C2%A0did%20not%20succeed.%20While%20recognizing%20the%20right%20of%20soldiers%20to%20plunder%2C%20Hastings%20believed%20that%20the%C2%A0distribution%20should%20have%20been%20done%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Company.%20Yet%20the%20fact%20of%20plunder%20and%C2%A0prize%20was%20not%20denied%2C%20even%20though%20Hastings%20argued%20in%20his%20defence%20that%20he%20did%20not%20give%20any%20direct%C2%A0order%20to%20plunder%20the%20fortress.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Major%20Popham%20stated%20before%20the%20House%20of%20Lords%C2%A0that%20Hastings%E2%80%99s%20private%20instructions%20were%20well%20known%2C%20and%20it%20was%20understood%20by%20the%20army%20to%20mean%C2%A0that%20they%20did%20indeed%20have%20the%20right%20to%20plunder.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20it%20was%20argued%20that%20Hastings%20would%C2%A0have%20to%20take%20responsibility%2C%20since%20plunder%20could%20be%20recognized%20as%20prize%20only%20if%20it%20followed%20a%20legal%C2%A0procedure%2C%20whereas%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Vidyadurg%20no%20such%20procedure%20was%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBritish%20spellings%20from%20the%20archives%2Frecords%20have%20been%20retained%20and%20end%20notes%20have%20been%20removed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERahul%20Govind%20teaches%20history%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Delhi.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710052034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10115615%2F16446.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Froyal-prerogative-the-british-empire-in-india-and-the-jurisprudence-of-plunder%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20Govind's%20book%20establishes%20the%20centrality%20of%20forms%20of%20royal%20authority%20to%20the%20conquests%20of%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20from%201600%20to%201900.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Froyal-prerogative-the-british-empire-in-india-and-the-jurispru