althcare%2C%20cars%2C%20computers%20and%20phones.%20More%20roads%20are%20built%2C%20buildings%20raised%2C%20clothes%20worn%2C%20toys%20and%20gadgets%20and%20appliances%20used.%20More%20people%20are%20traveling%20farther%20and%20more%20often.%20And%20the%20global%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product%E2%80%94possibly%20the%20most%20revered%20metric%20in%20all%20of%20human%20history%E2%80%94has%20been%20going%20up%20and%20up%20and%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGraphs%20of%20consumption%20or%20production%20of%20various%20commodities%20and%20goods%E2%80%94like%20sand%20or%20cement%2C%20steel%20or%20cars%2C%20houses%20or%20furniture%2C%20and%20a%20host%20of%20other%20things%E2%80%94as%20well%20as%20the%20size%20of%20the%20human%20population%2C%20emissions%20of%20industrial%20waste%2C%20or%20other%20metrics%20reflecting%20our%20use%20of%20energy%20and%20materials%2C%20nearly%20all%20indicate%20a%20strikingly%20similar%20growth%20pattern%20across%20time%3A%20around%20the%201950s%2C%20all%20these%20things%20began%20to%20accelerate.%20Geologists%2C%20anthropologists%2C%20and%20others%20call%20this%20astonishing%20trend%20the%20%3Cem%3EGreat%20Acceleration%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%20began%20two%20hundred%20years%20prior%20to%20this.%20So%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%2020th%20Century%20to%20fuel%20such%20a%20rush%20in%20the%20consumption%20of%20energy%20and%20materials%2C%20the%20associated%20pollution%20of%20air%2C%20water%2C%20and%20soil%2C%20and%20a%20dramatic%20acceleration%20in%20the%20extinction%20of%20species%20and%20loss%20of%20biodiversity%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112214%2F1280px-Anthropocene-GreatAccelerationSocioEconomicTrends-1750-2010.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3