5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecentralised%20Indian%20farming%20systems%20once%20provided%20more%20diversified%20diets%20based%20around%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournalofethnicfoods.biomedcentral.com%2Farticles%2F10.1186%2Fs42779-019-0011-9%5C%22%3Emillets%2C%20pulses%2C%20and%20rices%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20rural%20hunger%20still%20climbed%20as%20the%20population%20grew%2C%20soils%20were%20destroyed%20by%20more%20intensive%20cultivation%2C%20and%20cash%20crops%20were%20mandated%2C%20especially%20during%20European%20colonisation.%20Finally%20the%20Green%20Revolution%2C%20embarked%20in%201964%2C%20increased%20crop%20yields%20for%20three%20decades%2C%20making%20India%20self-sufficient%20in%20food%20production%20by%20the%201990s.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7611098%2F%5C%22%3Eyields%20per%20acre%20stopped%20rising%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20that%2C%20while%20the%20population%20and%20soil%20destruction%20did%20not%2C%20necessitating%20further%20farmland%20expansion%20and%20intensification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20dynamics%20continue%20today.%20Whether%20by%20drawing%20people%20into%20its%20programme%20voluntarily%20or%20enmeshing%20them%20without%20fair%20possibility%20for%20them%20to%20opt%20out%2C%20the%20goal%20of%20linking%20everybody%20into%20this%20hegemonic%20system%20of%20high%20consumption%20and%20waste%20is%20what%20we%20now%20call%20%E2%80%98development.%E2%80%99%20It%20has%20reduced%20the%20number%20of%20people%20living%20more%20nomadic%20or%20subsistence-agrarian%20lives%2C%20while%20increasing%20the%20numbers%20of%20potential%20workers%20and%20consumers%2C%20expanding%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20market.%20Promising%20such%20a%20goal%20is%20a%20universal%20good%2C%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99%20became%20a%20lauded%20program%20of%20governments%20everywhere%20and%20an%20altruistic%20vision%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20uncountable%20NGOs%2C%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20%E2%80%98lifting%20people%20out%20of%20poverty%2C%E2%80%99%20though%20it%20frequently%20has%20the%20opposite%20effect.%20According%20to%20environmentalist%20Ashish%20Kothari%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.planetcritical.com%2Fp%2Fan-alternative-india-ashish-kothari%23details%5C%22%3E60%20million%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20lost%20their%20lands%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%E2%80%98development.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Green%20Revolution%20is%20touted%20as%20one%20of%20its%20great%20successes.%20This%20program%20restored%20food%20access%20to%20villagers%E2%80%94who%E2%80%99d%20been%20brought%20to%20the%20point%20of%20starvation%20due%20to%20disastrously%20extractivist%20colonial%20policies%20coupled%20with%20rising%20populations%E2%80%94by%20applying%20artificial%20fertilisers%20and%20other%20petrochemicals%20to%20their%20fields.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20also%20destroyed%20their%20soils%20and%20locked%20some%20farmers%20into%20spiralling%20debt.%20And%20while%20the%20general%20expansion%20of%20energy%20consumption%20and%20rising%20GDP%20are%20considered%20%E2%80%98development%2C%E2%80%99%20these%20too%20have%20ultimately%20been%20built%20upon%20a%20limited%20trove%20of%20combustible%20fossils%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fto-the-pm-from-kaziranga-an-open-letter-decrying-displacement-human-rights-violations%5C%22%3Econtinuing%20dispossession%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20and%20other%20modes%20of%20environmental%20destruction.%20Yet%20choruses%20glorifying%20new%20feats%20of%20wealth%20and%20power%20continuously%20drown%20out%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20dispossessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2