e%20to%20tell%20ourselves.%20None%20of%20that%20would%20go%20anywhere%20without%20oil.%20And%E2%80%94let%E2%80%99s%20not%20fool%20ourselves%E2%80%94without%20oil%2C%20it%20will%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20376px)%2085vw%2C%20376px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22376%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896.jpg%20874w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896-219x300.jpg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896-746x1024.jpg%20746w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696598%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22516%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20combustible%20fossils%E2%80%94petroleum%2C%20coal%2C%20and%20gas%E2%80%94are%20gifts%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fa-planetary-perspective%5C%22%3Ethe%20late%20Paleozoic%20era%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20first%20trees%20grew%20and%20fell%20in%20heaps%2C%20when%20great%20blooms%20of%20plankton%20and%20algae%20sank%20under%20the%20silt%20of%20the%20seas.%20All%20their%20remains%2C%20collected%20together%20in%20mountainous%20quantities%20and%20pressed%20down%20over%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20years%2C%20encapsulate%20the%20stored%20energy%20of%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20years%20of%20sunlight%20that%20had%20fallen%20to%20Earth%20before%20the%20reign%20of%20the%20dinosaurs.%20That%20chemical%20potential%20had%20lain%20dormant%20in%20the%20belly%20of%20the%20Earth%2C%20taken%20out%20of%20circulation%20from%20the%20living%20systems%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20our%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20humans%20have%20resur