ock-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Choosing%20the%20right%20profession%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20families%20of%20Sim%2C%20Kartik%20and%20their%20dog%2C%20Everest%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20living%20in%20a%20van%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20bizarre.%20%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20a%20van%20gives%20them%20an%20illusion%20of%20us%20being%20homeless%20or%20not%20accomplished.%20So%20we%20had%20to%20educate%20them%20a%20lot%20on%20how%20many%20couples%20are%20out%20there%2C%20living%20a%20fulfilling%20life%20by%20exploring%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kartik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20their%20safety%2C%20their%20parents%20were%20also%20worried%20about%20how%20they%20would%20work.%20The%20duo%20started%20to%20look%20for%20more%20flexible%20roles.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20switched%20our%20career%20away%20from%20management%20roles%20to%20more%20technical%20ones.%20From%202018%20onwards%2C%20we%20were%20both%20working%20full-time%20remote%20jobs%20in%20our%20respective%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kartik%2C%20who%20is%20an%20IT%20consultant.%20Sim%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20works%20in%20digital%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20left%20for%20them%20now%20was%20to%20travel%20the%20world.%20The%20couple%2C%20along%20with%20Everest%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F185344%2Ftravel-arunachal-pradesh-duo-quit-job-electrify-villages-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20travelled%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20more%20than%2018%20countries%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Choose%20only%20the%20essentials%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20moving%20from%20a%20home%20to%20a%20van%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20need%20to%20be%20left%20behind%20like%20clothes%2C%20furniture%20and%20utensils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESim%20and%20Kartik%20suggest%20starting%20small%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20clothing.%20Then%20the%20couple%20moved%20on%20to%20the%20bigger%20th